dct_title_s: Tabula complectens totam Belgicam, Flandriam, Brabantiam, Selandiam, Holandiam, Frisiam, Hannoniam, Gelriam, etc. cum aliis quibusdam locis adiacentibus
dct_alternative_sm: Tabvla complectens totam Belgicam, Flandriam, Brabantiam, Selandiam, Holandiam, Frisiam, Hannoniam, Gelriam, etc. cvm aliis qvibvsdam locis adiacentibvs
dct_description_sm: North oriented toward upper right of sheet.
Index in center of map, in sea.
Decorative border and cartouche, compass rose, rhumb lines.
Pictorial vignettes of settlements, figures (including armored soldiers, horsemen), flora, fauna, ships, sea monsters.
